snippet.title: Intellivision Lives! - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
A quick look at Intellivision Lives!, a compilation that has many games from the original home console that rivalled the Atari 2600 and the Colecovision. It was also the first Intellivision compilation to see a release in Europe, as Activision's PS1 compilation was US exclusive.

Intellivision, Intellivision Lives (C) Atari
Developed by Realtime Associates
Published in PAL Regions by System 3 | Play It
Published in the US by Crave Entertainment
Also available on Xbox and GameCube
